Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:08.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接连着伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:21.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口难开 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:27.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渐次斑驳  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:34.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至终焉之河
