Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:56.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故乡迢迢  时之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无爱无心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:14.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻苍空
